    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Ethiopian-style hake asa wat</strong> with the <strong>cooked rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>sliced chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
